```plantuml
@startuml thill_kafkacap

actor Source
participant "AeronCaptureDevice" as AeronCD
participant "MulticastCaptureDevice" as MulticastCD
participant "WebsocketCaptureDevice" as WebsocketCD
participant "Kafka Topic (Capture)" as CaptureKafka
participant "Deduplicator" as Dedup
participant "CaptureQueue" as CaptureQueue
participant "Buffered Publisher" as BufferedPub
participant "Kafka Topic (Outbound)" as OutboundKafka

Source -> AeronCD: Capture Message
Source -> MulticastCD: Capture Message
Source -> WebsocketCD: Capture Message

AeronCD -> CaptureKafka: Write Message
MulticastCD -> CaptureKafka: Write Message
WebsocketCD -> CaptureKafka: Write Message

CaptureKafka -> Dedup: Consume Message
Dedup -> CaptureQueue: Deduplicate and Buffer Message

CaptureQueue -> BufferedPub: Retrieve Message
BufferedPub -> OutboundKafka: Publish Message

@enduml
```